reviewText: I like this movie It has my Favorite actor Andrew E and Its very Funny to watch I don't recommend this movie for kids though besides that Its AWESOME!

This movie is funny. It takes place at a university and it is a collection of funny short skits, mostly slapstick comedy. It is in Tagalog though and there are no english subtitles. So it is more a product for the Filipino community and not a typical foreign film with subtitles.
